<div id="ta195_85" class="block iDevice_content">
<div class="dentro_contenidos" style="display: block;" id="pagina_1">
<p>In this case, students face a <b>multiple matching</b> activity in which the aim is to show understanding of general gist, attitude, opinion, topic, place and so on.</p>
<p>Students will listen to five short monologues about the same topic and relate each one of them to the correct option out of a choice.</p>
<p>Tips:</p>
<ul>
<li>Before you listen, read each option carefully and pay attention to the keywords.</li>
<li>Listen for the main idea that the speakers are expressing.</li>
<li>Remember that there is only one correct answer although the speakers may mention words from other options.</li>
</ul>
</div>
